lead_paragraph: Cristiano Ronaldo's new five-year contract with Real Madrid which ties him to the Spanish club until the age of 36 will not be his last, he said on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Not My Last Contract With Real, Says Ronaldo
headline.main: Not My Last Contract With Real, Says Ronaldo
